➜重庆城口：荒山披“绿装”
http://www.sohu.com/a/431559086_255783	16560
<p><img src="//p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201113/93c45abaa09d408883ac3e57c7ea8de6.jpeg" /></p>
